{"id":1168,"parent_id":0,"book_id":8,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":1168,"title":"Symbolism","subtitle":"","short_title":"Symbolism","uri":"/scriptures/bd/symbolism","content":[["div",{"id":"t1","uri":"/scriptures/bd/symbolism.t1","order":".000.3784"},[".title","Symbolism"],["div",{"id":"p1","uri":"/scriptures/bd/symbolism.p1","order":".000.3785"},"The scriptures are rich in symbolism and figurative expression. Ceremonies and ordinances are symbolic in their performance, and all bear record of Jesus Christ (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/6.63"},"Moses 6:63"],"). Such symbolism is seen in sacrifice (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/9.11-15"},"Heb. 9:11–15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/5.7-8"},"Moses 5:7–8"],"); in the sacrament (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-mark/14.20-24"},["span.small","JST"],"Mark 14:20–24 [Appendix]"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/22.13-20"},"Luke 22:13–20"],"); and in baptism (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/6.1-6"},"Rom. 6:1–6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/128.12-13"},"D&C 128:12–13"],"). Biblical names especially are symbolic (see",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bd/christ-names-of"},"Christ, names of"]],"and",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bd/names-of-persons"},"Names of persons"]],"). The tabernacle ceremony was symbolic of eternal things (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8?span=8-10"},"Heb. 8–10"],"), as was the entire law of Moses, containing types and shadows of Christ (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/13.29-32"},"Mosiah 13:29–32"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/25.15"},"Alma 25:15"],"). For other symbolic items see",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/20.8-11"},"Ex. 20:8–11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/5.13-16"},"Matt. 5:13–16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/4.5"},"Jacob 4:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/37.38-45"},"Alma 37:38–45"],"."]]],"refs":null}
